<h2 id="readme">README</h2>

<p>We built a national parks directory using the National Park Service API. This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Listing of all national parks</li>
  <li>Individual parks page</li>
</ul>

<p>Each park page includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>About</li>
  <li>Contact</li>
  <li>Hours</li>
  <li>Activities</li>
  <li></li>
  <li>Map</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="data">Data</h2>

<p>Data used for this project:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.nps.gov/subjects/developer/api-documentation.htm">National parks API</a> (National Parks Service)</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.nps.gov/subjects/developer/api-documentation.htm">Google Maps API</a> (National Parks Service)</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="kudos">Kudos</h2>

<p>Big kudos to NPS for:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Maintaining a public repository of the data.</li>
</ul>

